account_name: LT Col Ratneshwar Singh / Bhavna Singh
message:
Greetings..
Yesterday reached Biba Aunty house at 12 pm and accompanied her to Inlaks Budhrani Hospital for an MRI. Both MRI and CT scan were done, and the doctors advised Aunty to take one month rest. We left the hospital at 5:30 PM, went to Camp to buy medicines and a leg band, and returned to Aunty house by 8 o'clock. Tomorrow have to collect MRI report.
